## 3. Networking Feature (Revised)

### Intent-First Entry

When users open the Network tab, they first select their **purpose**:

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│   What brings you here today?           │
│                                         │
│   ┌─────────┐  ┌─────────┐              │
│   │ 🔍      │  │ 📚      │              │
│   │ Hiring  │  │ Learning│              │
│   └─────────┘  └─────────┘              │
│                                         │
│   ┌─────────┐  ┌─────────┐              │
│   │ 🤝      │  │ ☕      │              │
│   │ Collab  │  │ Open    │              │
│   └─────────┘  └─────────┘              │
│                                         │
│   [Skip for now]                        │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

This intent:
- Filters who you see (matching intents prioritized)
- Shows in your profile when visible
- Creates natural conversation starters

### Contextual Triggers

Users see people based on **real context**, not generic browsing:

| Trigger | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Checked In Nearby** | Users at the same café location, visible for 30-60 mins |
| **Same Event Attendees** | People registered for the same event |
| **Similar Intent** | Users looking for what you offer (e.g., hiring ↔ looking) |
| **At Nearby Tables** | Physical proximity indicator (Table 5, Table 7) |

### Time-Boxed Visibility (Check-In)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│   Check In to Be Visible                │
│                                         │
│   📍 Bean & Gone Café                   │
│   🪑 Table: [___7___]                   │
│                                         │
│   Visibility duration:                  │
│   ○ 30 minutes                          │
│   ● 60 minutes                          │
│   ○ Until I check out                   │
│                                         │
│   Your intent: 🤝 Collaboration         │
│                                         │
│   [Check In Now]                        │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

Benefits:
- Creates urgency ("they're here now!")
- Reduces stale/ghost profiles
- Privacy-friendly (auto check-out)

### Connection Flow

```
See Profile → "Request to Connect" → (Optional) Add intro message →
Wait for acceptance → Chat unlocked → Schedule meeting (optional)
```

