## 4. Community Board (Revised - Focused Scope)

### Strict Post Types

Only 4 professional post types allowed:

| Type | Color | Example Use Case |
|------|-------|------------------|
| **🔍 Hiring** | Blue | "Looking for a part-time designer" |
| **📚 Learning** | Purple | "Anyone here experienced in AI/ML?" |
| **🤝 Collaboration** | Green | "Need a co-founder for my startup" |
| **📣 Event Discussion** | Orange | "Anyone going to the startup meetup?" |

### No Free-Form Social Posts

- ❌ No "Just had a great coffee!" posts
- ❌ No memes, opinions, or general updates
- ✅ Only professional, actionable content

### Post Creation Flow

```
[+] Create Post
    ↓
Select Type: [Hiring] [Learning] [Collab] [Event]
    ↓
Write your message (max 280 chars)
    ↓
Preview → Post
```

### Visual Distinction

Each post type has:
- Distinct accent color
- Type badge at top
- Author info + "Reply" action
- "Interested" count

