## 5. Meeting Review System (Trust-First)

### Dual-Blind Reveal

Ratings are only revealed **after both parties submit**:

```
You rate Sarah: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
Sarah rates you: (pending)
    ↓
Your rating: Hidden until Sarah submits
    ↓
[Both submitted]
    ↓
"Your meeting with Sarah was mutually positive! 🎉"
```

### Aggregated Trust Indicators (Not Raw Scores)

Instead of showing "4.2 stars", show:

| Indicator | Meaning |
|-----------|---------|
| ✅ **Verified Networker** | Completed 5+ meetings |
| 💬 **Recommended** | "Recommended by 3 of your connections" |
| ⭐ **Consistently Positive** | 90%+ positive ratings (no number) |
| 🆕 **New to Networking** | < 3 meetings (encourage first meetings) |

### Feedback Categories

After meeting, rate on:
- **Conversation Quality** (thumbs up/down)
- **Value Provided** (thumbs up/down)
- **Would Meet Again** (yes/no)

Optional: Short private note (not public).

### Privacy-First

- No public star ratings
- No visible negative feedback
- Only aggregated positive indicators shown
- Private feedback for personal improvement only

