## 7. Product Success Metrics

### Feature-to-Outcome Mapping

| Feature | Primary Metric | Secondary Metrics |
|---------|---------------|-------------------|
| **Ordering** | Order frequency per user | AOV, reorder rate |
| **Rewards** | Points redemption rate | Tier upgrades, repeat visits |
| **Networking** | Connections made per session | Check-in duration, messages sent |
| **Community** | Posts created per week | Replies, interested clicks |
| **Meetings** | Meetings scheduled | Completion rate, satisfaction score |
| **FTUE** | Onboarding completion rate | Time to first order |

### Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)

| KPI | Target | Why It Matters |
|-----|--------|----------------|
| **D7 Retention** | > 40% | Users return within 7 days |
| **Orders/User/Month** | > 3 | Healthy engagement |
| **Avg Check-In Duration** | 30-45 min | Networking is being used |
| **Connection Accept Rate** | > 60% | Quality connections |
| **Review Submission Rate** | > 70% | Trust system is adopted |
| **NPS** | > 50 | Users recommend the app |

### Success Signals Per Screen

| Screen | Success Signal |
|--------|----------------|
| Home | Tap on product within 10s |
| Rewards | Tier progress viewed |
| Network | Check-in completed |
| Community | Post or reply created |
| Profile | Completion > 80% |

